01:16:26.400 --> 01:16:31.658
US ahead if they’re bottlenecked on compute?
No, no. We've got Vera Rubin&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:16:31.658 --> 01:16:33.680
for the United States.
We have Vera Rubin for the United States.&nbsp;

