know, our share is growing, not decreasing.
The premise that even if we competed in China,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:20:20.560 --> 01:20:26.880
that we're going to lose that&nbsp;
market anyways… You're not&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:20:26.880 --> 01:20:33.200
